\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/bst_recenttrends.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalreserve.gov%2Fmonetarypolicy%2Fbst_recenttrends.htm&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cIwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=73173c0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/bst_recenttrends.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nBalance sheet 仲係縮緊，點睇到擴表？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"我都睇唔到有<br />\n<br />\n加速縮表就有<br />\n<br />\n外電引述6名消息人士透露，10月份美國財長姆紐欽曾私底下詢問債券交易商和投資者，是希望聯儲局通過加息還是加速「縮表」的方式來收緊貨幣政策。 <br />\n<br />\n實際上，無論縮表或加息，最終都體現到利率層面上。只是縮表更針對的是長期利率，因為聯儲局資產負債表的國債以長期為主，而加息則是通過買賣短期國債影響短期利率的操作；所以本質上兩者的差別不大。"},{"pid":"e56808f15db30b4e402edcc05bb3095a41473e82","tid":920501,"uid":62935,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"報紙講你就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利率期貨仲係下年加兩次大機會"},{"pid":"a9f1b0be0fe6eb14a243f467b85736d0833d0467","tid":920501,"uid":59746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ec50c81f7254345812abc22b262a1b3d5aaf52c","tid":920501,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5befd8e07845b792134a3d6c53d647674a0f256e","tid":920501,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"066efb1df27bff02243714f6e5b682b1f8870e2b","tid":920501,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"邊度睇到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/bs